WEBVTT

00:01:43.359 --> 00:01:44.359
Brother Chengwen.

00:01:49.400 --> 00:01:50.879
Do you really not want to see me that much?

00:01:52.400 --> 00:01:53.280
That's not it.

00:01:53.519 --> 00:01:54.159
I...

00:01:54.159 --> 00:01:55.400
just woke up.

00:01:55.400 --> 00:01:57.840
I'm just getting out of bed to stretch.

00:01:57.840 --> 00:01:59.040
Hahaha.

00:01:59.040 --> 00:01:59.840
Danger, danger!

00:02:00.120 --> 00:02:02.000
Leng Qingqiu's tender and gentle look...

00:02:02.079 --> 00:02:04.239
Anyone's heart would skip a beat seeing that!

00:02:07.319 --> 00:02:08.400
What are you laughing at?

00:02:11.039 --> 00:02:12.280
I almost forgot.

00:02:12.719 --> 00:02:14.400
You can hear my inner thoughts.

00:02:14.439 --> 00:02:15.639
Since you don't mind me,

00:02:15.840 --> 00:02:17.039
then from now on,

00:02:17.719 --> 00:02:19.240
we can be considered

00:02:19.240 --> 00:02:20.800
boyfriend and girlfriend.

00:02:21.280 --> 00:02:22.080
Chengwen.

00:02:22.479 --> 00:02:23.280
What's wrong?

00:02:23.400 --> 00:02:24.240
Ah.

00:02:24.680 --> 00:02:25.840
Are you feeling unwell?

00:02:26.840 --> 00:02:27.639
I'm fine.

00:02:27.680 --> 00:02:28.319
Mengyun.

00:02:28.319 --> 00:02:29.319
Why are you here?

00:02:30.000 --> 00:02:31.240
I came to get medicine for Grandpa.

00:02:32.039 --> 00:02:32.840
Mengyun,

00:02:33.000 --> 00:02:34.639
Brother Chengwen is my boyfriend now.

00:02:34.879 --> 00:02:35.680
Boyfriend?

00:02:36.400 --> 00:02:38.400
That's not something you can just decide on your own.

00:02:39.039 --> 00:02:39.919
Right, Chengwen?

00:02:46.000 --> 00:02:47.039
Ladies, please,

00:02:47.039 --> 00:02:48.840
just let me go.

00:02:49.840 --> 00:02:50.840
That's enough.

00:02:51.439 --> 00:02:53.000
Brother Chengwen chased me for three years.

00:02:53.240 --> 00:02:53.800
He's tired.

00:02:53.800 --> 00:02:55.199
So now it's my turn to chase him.

00:02:55.199 --> 00:02:56.639
And then we got together.

00:02:57.639 --> 00:02:58.400
Chengwen,

00:02:58.919 --> 00:02:59.680
didn't you want to have

00:02:59.680 --> 00:03:00.400
a family of three

00:03:00.400 --> 00:03:01.719
and live a happy life?

00:03:01.800 --> 00:03:02.599
I think

00:03:02.599 --> 00:03:03.639
we can arrange that now.

00:03:03.719 --> 00:03:04.400
Brother Chengwen,

00:03:04.400 --> 00:03:06.199
you said last night you'd take me to meet your mom.

00:03:06.479 --> 00:03:07.680
Let's go right now.

00:03:07.840 --> 00:03:09.080
M-my mom?

00:03:10.000 --> 00:03:10.840
Qingqiu,

00:03:11.280 --> 00:03:13.439
you and Chengwen are already in the past.

00:03:13.439 --> 00:03:15.000
Feelings have an expiration date.

00:03:15.000 --> 00:03:16.199
Doing all this now

00:03:16.199 --> 00:03:17.719
is completely meaningless.

00:03:36.439 --> 00:03:36.879
Mengyun,

00:03:36.879 --> 00:03:37.719
that's enough.

00:03:37.879 --> 00:03:39.199
Brother Chengwen is my boyfriend.

00:03:39.319 --> 00:03:40.439
You can't steal him away.

00:03:40.599 --> 00:03:41.400
Qingqiu,

00:03:41.439 --> 00:03:43.400
I remember Brother Chengwen didn't agree to that.

00:03:43.639 --> 00:03:44.159
Isn't

00:03:44.159 --> 00:03:44.479
that right?

00:03:44.599 --> 00:03:45.400
Chengwen?

00:03:46.039 --> 00:03:46.520
Chengwen!

00:03:46.520 --> 00:03:46.840
Chengwen!

00:03:46.840 --> 00:03:47.639
What are you all doing?

00:03:47.639 --> 00:03:49.120
You've made the patient like this!

00:03:49.520 --> 00:03:50.120
Get out!

00:03:50.120 --> 00:03:50.680
Get out!

00:03:51.240 --> 00:03:52.280
Don't disturb the patient's rest!

00:04:20.000 --> 00:04:20.800
Young Master

00:04:21.079 --> 00:04:22.680
Lu Chengwen's scheme to sow discord

00:04:23.000 --> 00:04:25.000
not only alienated the Leng father and daughter,

00:04:25.120 --> 00:04:27.040
but also broke through Leng Qingqiu's defenses,

00:04:27.319 --> 00:04:29.199
making her completely devoted to him.

00:04:29.439 --> 00:04:30.720
This man's scheming is so deep,

00:04:30.879 --> 00:04:32.000
it's absolutely outrageous.

00:04:32.399 --> 00:04:34.040
What exactly are you trying to do?

00:04:34.480 --> 00:04:36.519
Are you trying to stop me from uniting Haicheng?

00:04:37.000 --> 00:04:38.399
There are changes at the border now.

00:04:38.519 --> 00:04:39.720
Haicheng cannot fall into chaos.

00:04:40.439 --> 00:04:42.079
Keeping you alive

00:04:42.079 --> 00:04:43.600
will only lead to endless trouble.

00:04:43.920 --> 00:04:45.439
I will kill this scoundrel right now.

00:04:45.720 --> 00:04:48.680
Gu Zhantian will protect you all.

00:04:48.800 --> 00:04:50.199
Stop bothering me.

00:04:50.680 --> 00:04:51.480
Mom.

00:04:51.639 --> 00:04:53.079
I miss you so much.

00:04:53.800 --> 00:04:56.199
When will you recover from your illness?

00:04:58.319 --> 00:04:59.399
So full of tricks.

00:05:01.279 --> 00:05:02.079
Young Master.

00:05:02.120 --> 00:05:02.839
Why?

00:05:02.839 --> 00:05:04.000
Why do I feel

00:05:04.000 --> 00:05:05.639
such a deep sense of defeat?

00:05:05.680 --> 00:05:06.839
What is this?

00:05:07.120 --> 00:05:08.720
Anger out of humiliation after failing?

00:05:10.040 --> 00:05:11.040
How is that possible?

00:05:11.639 --> 00:05:13.279
I am the God of War at the border.

00:05:13.480 --> 00:05:15.000
How could I possibly fail?

00:05:15.519 --> 00:05:16.319
Right.

00:05:16.720 --> 00:05:18.439
I will not fail.

00:05:19.720 --> 00:05:20.639
Lu Chengwen,

00:05:22.839 --> 00:05:25.600
I will definitely defeat you fair and square.

00:05:29.000 --> 00:05:29.839
Xuening,

00:05:30.600 --> 00:05:31.519
let's go.

00:05:45.240 --> 00:05:46.040
Shihan.

00:05:46.120 --> 00:05:46.920
Mr. Lu,

00:05:47.000 --> 00:05:48.480
my mom's illness has relapsed.

00:05:48.600 --> 00:05:50.120
Dr. Xu said she needs surgery immediately.

00:05:50.199 --> 00:05:51.439
Can I take a day off?

00:05:52.680 --> 00:05:53.480
Of course.

00:05:54.079 --> 00:05:54.839
Don't worry.

00:05:54.839 --> 00:05:55.439
I believe

00:05:55.439 --> 00:05:56.199
with Xuejiao there,

00:05:56.199 --> 00:05:57.600
your mom will definitely be fine.

00:05:57.600 --> 00:05:58.199
Mr. Lu,

00:05:58.199 --> 00:05:59.480
I'm really scared.

00:06:00.079 --> 00:06:01.600
I'm afraid my mom will never wake up again.

00:06:02.240 --> 00:06:03.199
I happen to be at the hospital right now.

00:06:03.199 --> 00:06:04.240
I'll come find you.

00:06:13.839 --> 00:06:14.600
Mr. Lu,

00:06:15.120 --> 00:06:16.240
you're here.

00:06:18.319 --> 00:06:19.480
I'm here.

00:06:20.920 --> 00:06:23.199
I ran into Mr. Gu in the hospital corridor.

00:06:23.439 --> 00:06:24.879
Originally, Mr. Gu agreed

00:06:24.879 --> 00:06:26.600
to perform a full-body surgery on my mom.

00:06:26.600 --> 00:06:27.120
But

00:06:27.120 --> 00:06:30.199
Dr. Xu is already waiting in the operating room.

00:06:31.000 --> 00:06:31.839
So...

00:06:34.399 --> 00:06:35.319
I'm screwed.

00:06:35.879 --> 00:06:38.360
The plot of Gu Zhantian saving Jiang Shihan's mom

00:06:38.360 --> 00:06:39.720
is completely ruined.

00:06:40.240 --> 00:06:41.839
Xu Xuejiao was entrusted by me,

00:06:42.279 --> 00:06:43.839
stealing his highlight moment.

00:06:49.000 --> 00:06:49.839
You...

00:06:49.839 --> 00:06:50.800
Have a seat.

00:06:51.040 --> 00:06:51.839
Sit down.

00:06:52.879 --> 00:06:53.399
Since

00:06:53.399 --> 00:06:54.439
Brother Zhantian is here,

00:06:54.480 --> 00:06:56.480
I believe your mom will be fine very soon.

00:06:57.879 --> 00:06:59.000
I'll... I'll get going now.

00:06:59.000 --> 00:06:59.600
Mr. Lu,

00:06:59.600 --> 00:07:00.519
don't go.

00:07:01.839 --> 00:07:02.879
I'm scared.

00:07:06.240 --> 00:07:06.959
I'd better...

00:07:06.959 --> 00:07:08.000
I'd better go.

00:07:14.519 --> 00:07:15.079
I'll... I'll stay here.

00:07:15.079 --> 00:07:15.879
I'll stay here.

00:07:27.439 --> 00:07:28.079
Dr. Xu.

00:07:28.079 --> 00:07:29.199
How is my mom?

00:07:29.199 --> 00:07:30.120
The surgery was a success.

00:07:30.240 --> 00:07:31.519
She'll be out after the stitches.

00:07:31.519 --> 00:07:32.480
You can rest assured.

00:07:32.680 --> 00:07:33.079
Yeah.

00:07:33.079 --> 00:07:33.800
Miss Xu.

00:07:33.800 --> 00:07:35.279
Truly a renowned doctor in Haicheng.

00:07:35.399 --> 00:07:37.439
I'll say thank you on Shihan's behalf.

00:07:37.800 --> 00:07:39.240
Who are you to Shihan?

00:07:39.439 --> 00:07:40.600
Why should you thank me for her?

00:07:41.040 --> 00:07:43.040
Besides, I was asked by Brother Chengwen.

00:07:43.279 --> 00:07:44.720
Brother Chengwen is the one who should say that.

00:07:46.120 --> 00:07:48.399
Are you delirious from the surgery?

00:07:48.839 --> 00:07:49.839
What nonsense are you spouting?

00:07:50.720 --> 00:07:51.800
My little troublemaker.

00:07:51.800 --> 00:07:52.839
Keep it down.

00:07:53.000 --> 00:07:54.079
Once Gu Zhantian leaves,

00:07:54.079 --> 00:07:56.040
you can do whatever you want.

00:07:57.279 --> 00:07:58.079
Mr. Gu.

00:07:58.680 --> 00:08:00.439
Thank you for waiting with me for so long.

00:08:00.800 --> 00:08:01.839
It's getting late.

00:08:01.839 --> 00:08:03.040
Why don't you head back first?

00:08:04.720 --> 00:08:05.519
Okay.

00:08:05.839 --> 00:08:07.120
Let me know if you need anything later.

00:08:08.480 --> 00:08:09.279
Miss Xu.

00:08:09.439 --> 00:08:10.639
You've worked hard today.

00:08:20.040 --> 00:08:20.639
Dr. Xu.

00:08:20.639 --> 00:08:22.279
When will my mom wake up?

00:08:22.839 --> 00:08:23.279
Probably

00:08:23.279 --> 00:08:24.839
in about an hour or so.

00:08:26.120 --> 00:08:26.920
Shihan.

00:08:27.279 --> 00:08:28.800
I'll approve some paid leave for you.

00:08:28.839 --> 00:08:30.680
Go home and take good care of your mom.

00:08:30.720 --> 00:08:31.759
Once she's fully recovered,

00:08:31.759 --> 00:08:32.519
you can come back to work.

00:08:32.639 --> 00:08:33.519
Thank you, Mr. Lu.

00:08:41.200 --> 00:08:41.840
What's wrong?

00:08:41.840 --> 00:08:42.919
The surgery was too exhausting.

00:08:42.919 --> 00:08:43.879
The surgery was too exhausting, huh?

00:08:44.000 --> 00:08:44.240
Let's go.

00:08:44.240 --> 00:08:45.120
I'll take you home.

00:08:45.639 --> 00:08:46.440
To your place.

00:08:47.039 --> 00:08:49.240
My dad hates it when I go into surgery.

00:08:50.240 --> 00:08:51.039
No way.

00:08:51.399 --> 00:08:52.919
Didn't you say once Gu Zhantian leaves,

00:08:52.919 --> 00:08:54.639
I could do whatever I want?

00:08:56.320 --> 00:08:58.799
Someone's going back on their word, huh?

00:08:58.879 --> 00:09:00.799
I don't think Gu Zhantian has gone far.

00:09:00.840 --> 00:09:01.919
Help, pervert!

00:09:05.519 --> 00:09:06.720
Shh, shh, shh!

00:09:26.879 --> 00:09:28.279
When are you finally leaving?

00:09:36.080 --> 00:09:37.440
My legs are sore.

00:09:54.840 --> 00:09:55.840
If you're massaging, just massage.

00:09:55.840 --> 00:09:56.600
Don't make those

00:09:56.600 --> 00:09:58.039
weird noises, okay?

00:10:00.279 --> 00:10:01.399
I can't take it anymore.

00:10:02.480 --> 00:10:03.399
Who can't take it?

00:10:03.639 --> 00:10:05.600
I'm the number one bad boy in Haicheng.

00:10:05.600 --> 00:10:07.000
I've seen it all.

00:10:07.600 --> 00:10:08.399
But you,

00:10:09.480 --> 00:10:10.279
aren't you afraid

00:10:10.279 --> 00:10:11.480
something might happen?

00:10:11.639 --> 00:10:12.679
Then bring it on.

00:10:13.600 --> 00:10:14.399
I...

00:10:15.240 --> 00:10:16.440
Bring what on?

00:10:16.919 --> 00:10:17.919
You're a girl.

00:10:17.919 --> 00:10:19.480
Mind your image, will you?

00:10:19.679 --> 00:10:21.240
What's wrong with being a girl?

00:10:22.279 --> 00:10:23.240
Brother Chengwen.

00:10:23.600 --> 00:10:25.120
Do you want me

00:10:25.120 --> 00:10:26.480
to train you a bit?

00:10:28.879 --> 00:10:30.080
Don't go too far.

00:10:30.279 --> 00:10:31.519
Do you hate me?

00:10:34.840 --> 00:10:35.519
I don't exactly

00:10:35.519 --> 00:10:36.720
hate you.

00:10:37.200 --> 00:10:39.000
You used to ignore me.

00:10:39.240 --> 00:10:40.200
But recently, you suddenly

00:10:40.399 --> 00:10:42.039
started clinging to me.

00:10:42.039 --> 00:10:43.840
This is too big of a change.

00:10:44.320 --> 00:10:45.120
You

00:10:46.720 --> 00:10:49.639
don't like me clinging to you?

00:10:52.000 --> 00:10:52.799
I don't like it.

00:10:53.039 --> 00:10:54.080
Not one bit.

00:10:54.320 --> 00:10:55.080
Then have a drinking contest with me.

00:10:55.080 --> 00:10:55.519
If you win,

00:10:55.519 --> 00:10:56.679
I'll never bother you again.

00:11:06.600 --> 00:11:07.399
No.

00:11:14.879 --> 00:11:15.639
Help, pervert!

00:11:17.919 --> 00:11:18.720
Help, pervert!

00:11:20.279 --> 00:11:21.080
Help, pervert!